if update_out_of_domain:

neuron.out_of_domain_min_f1_score is equal to 0.9, which is pretty low threshold for any quality solution. If you can't reach 0.9 F1 score your miner won't survive the competition anyway, so you just better to use local validator until you reach the certain level of accuracy
